# Allowed Domains Configuration
# ===============================
# This file configures which domains the Claude container can access.
# Copy this file to `.claude/allowed-domains.txt` to customize network access.
#
# Format:
#   - One domain per line
#   - Lines starting with # are comments
#   - Empty lines are ignored
#   - Domains are resolved to IPs via DNS at container startup
#
# Note: GitHub IP ranges are always fetched dynamically from api.github.com/meta
# and do not need to be listed here.

# ----------------------------------------
# GitHub (automatically included)
# ----------------------------------------
# GitHub IPs are fetched dynamically from the GitHub API.
# You don't need to add github.com or api.github.com here.

